Class PlainWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • MWC.GUI.PlainWrapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Plottable>, Editable, Exportable, Plottable, Renamable, SupportsPropertyListeners
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    BuoyPatternWrapper, ChartBoundsWrapper, CoreFormatItemListener, DynamicTrackShapeWrapper, FixWrapper, GTrack, HideLayerFormatListener, LabelWrapper, LightweightTrackWrapper, LocationWrapper, NarrativeWrapper, ShapeWrapper, SnailDrawTacticalContact.PlottableWrapperWithTimeAndOverrideableColor, TacticalDataWrapper, TrackNameAtEndFormatListener

    public abstract class PlainWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements Plottable, java.io.Serializable, Exportable, SupportsPropertyListeners, Renamable
    This class shows all the responsibilities of the wrapper items. In particular the fact that the data items should be able to describe themselves, and create/fill which shows/describes the raw data
